message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which we believe is truly exceptional. It's designed to enhance your daily life with its unique features and high-quality craftsmanship. Considering its value and benefits, I propose a price of $120 for it. This offer includes a 30-day satisfaction guarantee, where you can return the product if it doesn't meet your expectations. I trust this price reflects the superior quality and utility of the product, and I look forward to your positive response.
